title: Dosa Houze
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Dec 2014 re-opened here after move from 1 Victoria Rd. Indian food restaurant once vegetarian but switched to adding meat. At lunch the prices are inexpensive, and you could get a vegetable curry with either dosa, rice, or naan. Dinner menu prices are moderate has several vegetarian suitable dishes. Uses dairy so ask if vegan.
streetAddress: 307 Linthorpe Rd, Old Yorkshire Bank Building
